# Site Architecture

## Core Pages
- /: Home page - Welcome to the Smart Attendance System
- /setup-wizard: Setup wizard for first-time configuration

## Application SPA Routes
- /dashboard: User dashboard - Access attendance records and manage users
- /login: User login - Dashboard Login
- /mark-attendance: Mark attendance in the SPA
- /attendance: View attendance in the SPA
- /session: Active attendance session in the SPA
- /add-photos: Add user photos in the SPA
- /employees/register: Register a new employee in the SPA
- /train: Train facial recognition models

## Documentation
- /docs: Technical documentation

## Admin & Dashboards
- /admin/evaluation/: Admin evaluation dashboard
- /admin/ablation/: Admin ablation results
- /admin/failures/: Admin failure analysis
- /admin/health/: Admin system health
- /admin/attendance-dashboard/: Admin attendance dashboard
- /admin/attendance-dashboard/export/: Admin attendance export
- /admin/fairness/: Admin fairness dashboard
- /admin/recognition-trends/: Admin recognition accuracy trends
- /admin/threshold-profiles/: Admin threshold profiles management
- /admin/threshold-profiles/create/: Admin threshold profile create
- /admin/threshold-profiles/import/: Admin threshold profile import
- /django-admin/: Django Admin Interface

## API Endpoints
- /api/threshold/: Threshold profile API
- /api/v1/auth/login/: Auth Login API
- /api/v1/auth/refresh/: Auth Refresh API
- /api/v1/auth/verify/: Auth Verify API
- /api/v1/users/: Users API
- /api/v1/attendance/: Attendance API
- /monitoring/metrics/: Monitoring metrics API
